<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title><%= pageTitle %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/app-shell.css" />
    <style>
        .survival-layout { width:min(1180px, calc(100% - 24px)); margin:0 auto; }
        .survival-topbar { display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:16px; padding:18px 0 6px; }
        .survival-brand { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:12px; color:var(--app-text); text-decoration:none; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:.16em; }
        .survival-mark { width:40px; height:40px; border-radius:14px; display:grid; place-items:center; background:linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(242,182,90,.22), rgba(125,211,252,.22)); }
        .survival-meta { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px; color:var(--app-muted); }
        .survival-chip { display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:8px; padding:7px 12px; border-radius:999px; background:rgba(242,182,90,.10); border:1px solid rgba(242,182,90,.18); color:#ffd79d; font-size:.8rem; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:.08em; }
        .survival-grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:1.2fr .8fr; gap:18px; margin-top:10px; }
        .survival-actions { display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:12px; margin-top:20px; }
        .survival-stats { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(2, minmax(0,1fr)); gap:14px; }
        .survival-stat { padding:16px; background:rgba(255,255,255,.03); }
        .survival-stat-label { color:var(--app-muted); font-size:.78rem; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:.08em; }
        .survival-stat-value { margin-top:8px; font-size:1.45rem; font-weight:700; }
        @media (max-width: 900px) {
            .survival-grid,
            .survival-stats { grid-template-columns:1fr; }
            .survival-topbar { flex-direction:column; align-items:flex-start; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="app-page">
    <div class="app-layout survival-layout">
        <header class="survival-topbar">
            <a class="survival-brand" href="/survival-admin/dashboard"><span class="survival-mark">O</span><span>SURVIVAL ADMIN</span></a>
            <div class="survival-meta">
                <span class="survival-chip">Current Server: <%= currentServerId %></span>
                <span><%= survivalAdminAccount?.fullName || "Survival Admin" %></span>
                <form method="post" action="/survival-admin/signout">
                    <button class="app-link-btn" type="submit">Sign Out</button>
                </form>
            </div>
        </header>

        <section class="survival-grid">
            <div class="app-panel">
                <div class="survival-chip">Outage-Safe Control Plane</div>
                <h1>Survival Admin Dashboard</h1>
                <p class="app-copy">Use this workspace when Primary DB access is unavailable or when you need a dedicated failover control panel. It is meant for live strategy continuity, ownership review, and recovery operations only.</p>
                <div class="survival-actions">
                    <a class="app-solid-btn" href="/survival-admin/running-users">Open Running Users</a>
                    <a class="app-ghost-btn" href="/dashboard">Back To Normal Dashboard</a>
                </div>
                <div class="survival-actions" style="margin-top:12px;">
                    <a class="app-ghost-btn" href="https://optionyze.onrender.com/survival-admin/signin" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Render Survival Admin</a>
                    <a class="app-ghost-btn" href="https://optionyze-production.up.railway.app/survival-admin/signin" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Railway Survival Admin</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="app-panel">
                <div class="survival-stats">
                    <div class="app-stat survival-stat">
                        <div class="survival-stat-label">Access Mode</div>
                        <div class="survival-stat-value">Survival Admin</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="app-stat survival-stat">
                        <div class="survival-stat-label">Scope</div>
                        <div class="survival-stat-value">Live Control</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="app-stat survival-stat">
                        <div class="survival-stat-label">Strategy Access</div>
                        <div class="survival-stat-value">Disabled</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="app-stat survival-stat">
                        <div class="survival-stat-label">Primary Use</div>
                        <div class="survival-stat-value">Takeover / Handback</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="survival-actions" style="margin-top:18px; flex-direction:column; align-items:flex-start;">
                    <div class="survival-stat-label">Operator Steps</div>
                    <div class="app-copy" style="margin:0;">1. Check running users and current owner.</div>
                    <div class="app-copy" style="margin:0;">2. During outage, let the owner continue or use takeover on the standby server if needed.</div>
                    <div class="app-copy" style="margin:0;">3. After recovery, confirm ownership has stabilized before any handback action.</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
